ECONOMIC_OPERATORS_PERSONAL_SITUATION.P: — statement of the economic operator that in the last 5 years he has not been pronounced a final verdict for participation in a criminal organization, corruption, fraud or money laundering,
— confirmation that no bankruptcy procedure has been initiated by a competent authority,
— confirmation that no liquidation procedure has been initiated by a competent authority,
— confirmation of paid taxes, contributions and other public fees from the competent authority of the country where the economic operator is registered,

— a certificate from the Register of penalties for committed criminal acts of legal entities that it has not been pronounced secondary penalty ban on participation in public call procedures, awarding public procurement contracts and contracts for public private partnership,

— a certificate from the register of penalties for committed criminal acts of legal entities that it has not been pronounced secondary punishment temporary or permanent ban on performing a particular activity,
— Confirmation that a final verdict has not been pronounced a misdemeanor sanction — ban on performing profession, activity or duty, that is, a temporary ban on performing a particular activity,
— Document for registered activity — DEP form or certificate for registered activity document for wholesale of medicinal products in accordance with the law on medicines and medical devices.

T_CAPACITY_INFORMATION.P: For registered medical devices — the economic operator has to provide for the offered goods approval for the placing on the market of a medical device or temporary or permanent approval for parallel importation, according to the law on medicines and medical devices.

For unregistered medical devices — The economic operator shall provide for the offered goods a Document that is permitted import (approval for interventional import) in accordance with the Law on medicines and medical devices. Mandatory submission of prospect materials for the offered goods with detailed qualitative and others characteristics of the goods that are the subject of procurement, and the marking of the offered, and mandatory submission of samples for the goods offered.
